        <abstract> 
<p>Unable to comment on F. Lloyd’s criticism of Francis Galton’s <hi rend="italic">Hereditary genius</hi> [?<hi rend="italic">A scientific view of Mr Galton’s theories of heredity</hi> (1876)].</p> 
            <p>Sorry about Lloyd’s health.</p>
            <p>Does not care much about abuse or fame, an advantage of age.</p>
        </abstract>
